name: Maureen
content:
Maureen was a female Human who lived during the waning years of the Galactic Republic.
In about 32 BBY, Maureen got a job working in the Space Monkey Caf√©, a bar that was located in the city of Bayonard, on the planet Cularin. She had worked there two weeks when the heroes of Cularin visited the bar, while they were investigating the disappearance of Selima DeWitt.
